Subject: drm/amd/display: Add I2C escape to support query device exist.
Git-commit: a0248d543bbf2a977e7e6d9966ce8d96f6e5c358
Patch-mainline: v5.18-rc1
References: jsc#PED-1166 jsc#PED-1168 jsc#PED-1170 jsc#PED-1218 jsc#PED-1220 jsc#PED-1222 jsc#PED-1223 jsc#PED-1225

[How]
1. Search OEM I2C info from BIOS and compare with input parameter.
2. If BIOS doesn't record it, just try to read one byte.

